data.description: NEW PRICE!!!Come Fall In LOVE! Upon entering this BEAUTIFUL home you will notice just how meticulous the owners are and how much they LOVE their home. First floor features newer high end laminate floors( so does the 2nd floor), Cozy living room with decorative fireplace. Kitchen offers ample cabinet space, center island with sink, Stainless steel appliances. Dining room with beautiful built ins. 1st floor laundry and Full bath. Upstairs you will find 2 generously sized bedrooms with plenty of closet space and lots of natural light. Most recent updates include HVAC System(23) and New Roof(21). Enjoy the fenced in side yard and the perks of a corner lot and off street parking. Just a few blocks from Nationwide Childrens. This home is truly one you will not want to miss.
